    public class PackageOwnedStereotypeMatcher
extends BaseMatcher<PackageOwnedStereotypeMatch>
    Generated pattern matcher API of the org.eclipse.viatra.integration.uml.derivedfeatures.packageOwnedStereotype pattern, providing pattern-specific query methods.

    Use the pattern matcher on a given model via on(ViatraQueryEngine), e.g. in conjunction with ViatraQueryEngine#on(Notifier).

    Matches of the pattern will be represented as PackageOwnedStereotypeMatch.

    Original source: 

     (packagedElement- >select(oclIsKindOf(Stereotype))- >collect(oclAsType(Stereotype))- >asSet())
 
  @Surrogate(feature = "ownedStereotype")
  @QueryExplorer(checked = false)
 pattern packageOwnedStereotype(
     self : Package,
     temp2 : Stereotype
 ) {
     Stereotype(stereotype);
     temp1 == stereotype;
     Package.packagedElement(self, packageableElement);
     temp1 == packageableElement;
     temp2 == temp1;
 }
